description:
3D printing is quickly becoming a new outlet for 3D enthusiasts everywhere to transform what used to be relegated to the monitor and screen into real, tangible assets. There are many methods for creating 3D prints of your models using a wide range of software; this VTC QuickStart! course will take you through one possible workflow. From sketching, to modeling in modo, to submitting a model to an online service provider, author Dwayne Ferguson will show you how to bring your models to life! This title is a self-paced software training course delivered via pre-recorded video. We do not provide additional information outside of the posted content.

Work files for this course can be downloaded from the first lecture.
title: QuickStart! - 3D Printing
